### Enrichment
2026 camping checklists from REI and OutdoorGearLab suggest missing items: first aid kit, fire-starting materials, water filtration, insect repellent, sunscreen, camp stove, basic cookware, multi-tool. Also recommended: moisture-wicking base layers, rain jacket. Existing list is solid for cold-weather hammock camping but could benefit from Food/Cooking and Safety sections.

